        "translations": {
          "en": "Muhammad ibn Musa ibn al-Mutawakkil (may God be pleased with him) narrated to us. He said: Muhammad ibn Yahya al-Attar narrated to us from Muhammad ibn Ahmad ibn Yahya ibn Imran al-Ashari, from Muhammad ibn Isa ibn Ubayd, from Sulayman ibn Rashid, from his father, from Muawiya ibn Ammar who said:",
